        Represents wheel distance in millimeters. Some cars may not have individual sensors on each wheel. If a value is not available, Long.MAX_VALUE will be reported.       • onCarDisconnected

        public void onCarDisconnected()
        从类复制的说明: CarManagerBase
        Handle disconnection of car service (=crash). As car service has crashed already, this call should only clean up any listeners / callbacks passed from client. Clearing object passed to car service is not necessary as car service has crashed. Note that Car*Manager will not work any more as all binders are invalid. Client should re-create all Car*Managers when car service is restarted.
        指定者:
        onCarDisconnected 在类中 CarManagerBase

      • registerListener

        public boolean registerListener(CarSensorManager.OnSensorChangedListener listener,
                                int sensorType,
                                int rate)
                         throws CarNotConnectedException,
                                java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
        Register CarSensorManager.OnSensorChangedListener to get repeated sensor updates. Multiple listeners can be registered for a single sensor or the same listener can be used for different sensors. If the same listener is registered again for the same sensor, it will be either ignored or updated depending on the rate.

        参数:
        listener -
        sensorType - sensor type to subscribe.
        rate - how fast the sensor events are delivered. It should be one of SENSOR_RATE_FASTEST, SENSOR_RATE_FAST, SENSOR_RATE_UI, SENSOR_RATE_NORMAL. Rate may not be respected especially when the same sensor is registered with different listener with different rates. Also, rate might be ignored when vehicle property raises events only when the value is actually changed, for example SENSOR_TYPE_PARKING_BRAKE will raise an event only when parking brake was engaged or disengaged.
        返回:
        if the sensor was successfully enabled.
        抛出:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - for wrong argument like wrong rate
        java.lang.SecurityException - if missing the appropriate permission
        CarNotConnectedException
